<summary>This is a REST API implementation of a trip management system similar to MakeMyTrip/Yatra that:Main Purpose:- Provides booking and management of trips, packages, buses, hotels and related travel servicesNetwork Attack Surfaces:- REST API endpoints exposed on port 8888- MySQL database connectivity- Swagger UI documentation interface at /swagger-ui/- Session-based authentication systemKey Networked Features:- Customer/Driver/Admin authentication with session tokens- CRUD operations for bookings, user management, and travel services- API endpoints for packages, bookings, routes, hotels and feedback- Multi-user system with role-based access controlThe application exposes significant attack surface through its REST API interface and database connectivity, with authentication being a critical security control point.</summary>